owner.name: Spectrum Detection
owner.description:
Divide the audio spectrum range (0 Hz to 22050 Hz) into 8 output bands, and detect the magnitude of each band in a range between 0 and 255. 
You can use the output values to animate or transform 2D objects.

owner.name: Combine
